ttack. At night, it burrows into the desert sand to sleep."},{"version":"sun","text":"It can roll its body into a ball. It moves through the desert by rolling at high speeds."},{"version":"moon","text":"It usually makes its home in deserts and arid zones, where rain does not fall. It digs holes to catch Bug-type Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It lives in areas of limited rainfall. When danger approaches, it curls up into a ball to protect its soft stomach."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"When its skin gets wrinkled from moisture, it heads for a volcano. It lies flat on a spot with a lot of geothermal heat and dries itself out."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its body is dry. When it gets cold at night, its hide is said to become coated with a fine dew."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its body is dry. When it gets cold at night, its hide is said to become coated with a fine dew."},{"version":"sword","text":"It loves to bathe in the grit of dry, sandy areas. By sand bathing, the Pok\u00e9mon rids itself of dirt and moisture clinging to its body."},{"version":"shield","text":"It burrows into the ground to create its nest. If hard stones impede its tunneling, it uses its sharp claws to shatter them and then carries on digging."}],"evo":{"name":"sandshrew","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"sandslash","level":1,"min_level":22,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/27.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubuse